title: Arwyn Manor Apts...NY Style...Spacious Studio..CALL NOW!
posting_body: ["Feel right at home at Arwyn Manor Apartments, a beautiful 1920's Art Deco style apartment building in Los Angeles, CA.", "Perfectly situated in hip Koreatown, you're just minutes away from everything you need such as the subway, Wilton Theater, coffee shops and UCLA!", 'All this and more can be found at Arwyn Manor.', 'Choose from our newly renovated studios and one bedroom floor plans, all of which include maple cabinets in the kitchen, granite counter tops, hardwood floors, tile floors in baths, spacious walk-in closets, and scenic views of downtown LA skyline.', 'Each apartment is brimming with amenities designed to make you feel at home.', 'Arwyn Manor brings amenities together with a central location that make life richer.', 'Residents enjoy the on-site laundry center, gated access, elevator, on-call maintenance, beautiful landscaping, professional management, and more.', 'Pets are welcome so bring the whole family!', 'Come home to Arwyn Manor Apartments and live the life you deserve.', 'For more information, please see <URL>', 'Cats allowed with an additional $200 deposit and dogs with an additional $300 deposit.', 'Professionally Managed by Statewide Enterprises, Inc.', 'To view a virtual tour of unit 605 - Studio - <URL>', 'OPEN HOUSE:', 'Thursday- 1:00pm-5pm', 'Friday- 9:00am-5pm', 'Saturday-8:00am-10:00am.', '-Quoted security deposit is on approved credit.', '-6 or 12 month - Six month lease available with $200 monthly surcharge.', 'Pictures in this ad are a representation and may not reflect the actual apartment that is currently available.', 'The rent, deposit, concession and terms listed in this ad are only valid for the actual date that this ad was initially posted.']
